          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2022-09-13 13:34:17" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>(a figurative extension of meaning of {L:ἀρνίον&lt;SDBG:ἀρνίον:000000&gt;}[a] ‘lamb,’ {D:4.25}) a follower of Christ, with the implication of helplessness and dependence</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>a person who is like a lamb</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>Compare {D:11.30} and {D:11.31}.</Comments>
            </LEXSense>
